
'''中威尔士'''（威尔士语：Canolbarth Cymru）指的是[[威尔士|威尔士]]的中部地区。[[威爾斯議會|威爾斯議會]]中的中威尔士地区委员会所關心的地區包括[[锡尔迪金|锡尔迪金]]、[[波伊斯|波伊斯]]和[[格温内斯|格温内斯]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=National Assembly for Wales. Mid Wales Regional Committee (July 2003 - March 2005)|url=http://www.assemblywales.org/bus-home/bus-committees/bus-committees-second/bus-committees-second-mwr-home/bus-committees-second-mwr-committee.htm|accessdate=2009-10-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081013131546/http://www.assemblywales.org/bus-home/bus-committees/bus-committees-second/bus-committees-second-mwr-home/bus-committees-second-mwr-committee.htm|archivedate=2008-10-13}}</ref>。[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]所定义的中威尔士與中威尔士地区委员会關注的地區類似<ref>{{Cite web|title=BBC Wales - Mid Wales|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/mid/|accessdate=2009-10-30|archive-date=2004-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040831112845/http://www.bbc.co.uk/wales/mid/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{link-en|威尔士空间规划|Town and country planning in Wales}}定義的中威尔士包括[[锡尔迪金|锡尔迪金]]和[[波伊斯|波伊斯]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Welsh Assembly Government - Central Wales|url=http://wales.gov.uk/location/central_wales/?lang=en|accessdate=2009-10-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090409200456/http://wales.gov.uk/location/central_wales/?lang=en|archivedate=2009-04-09}}</ref>。如果將中威尔士的概念限制在[[锡尔迪金|锡尔迪金]]和[[波伊斯|波伊斯]]，则中威尔士的面积为6962平方公里。

中威尔士的地形以[[坎布里安山脈|坎布里安山脈]]为主<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/tm_headline=-the--lost-land--of-wales-aiming-to-step-out-of-the-shadow-of-snowdon--&method=full&objectid=18023663&siteid=50082-name_page.html|title=Western Mail|author=Williams|first=Sally|date=1 November 2006|work=Cambrian Mountains campaign launched|accessdate=2009-10-30|archive-date=2012-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007211820/http://www.walesonline.co.uk/news/wales-news/tm_headline%3D-the--lost-land--of-wales-aiming-to-step-out-of-the-shadow-of-snowdon--%26method%3Dfull%26objectid%3D18023663%26siteid%3D50082-name_page.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中威尔士是一个人口稀少的农村地区，经济依赖[[农业|农业]]和小企业<ref>{{Cite web|title=National Assembly for Wales. Report from the Mid Wales Regional Committee.|url=http://www.assemblywales.org/394F67450006AD660000210800000000.pdf|accessdate=2009-10-30|date=June 2009|archive-date=2012-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120222013319/http://www.assemblywales.org/394F67450006AD660000210800000000.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[锡尔迪金|锡尔迪金]]和[[波伊斯|波伊斯]]兩地的人口密度只有30人/平方公里。

